description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute FULL BODY HIIT Workout | The Body Coach TV' from the channel The Body Coach TV by Joe Wicks.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: 20 moves | 40 seconds work | 20 seconds rest

Walkouts with press up
Squat pulses
Lateral plank walk with push up
Kick throughs
Run on the spot
Bear crawls
Burpee shuffle
Crab toe touches
Lateral run with jump
90ยบ squat jumps
Bear crawl 2 push ups
Split squat R
Split squat L
Floor arm circles
Hand release push ups
Wide spider climbers

Lunge jumps

Reverse lunge knee drive R
